condition.narrative: Finance Agreement :Annual Implementation Plan | Description :Ningxia shall furnish to the Bank a final annual implementation plan,including Bank's comments, by December 31, and implement the project according to the annual implementation plan. | Frequency:Yearly

Finance Agreement :Cultural Heritage | Description :Ningxia shall take or cause to be taken all such action as shall be necessaryin the implementation of the Project to protect cultural heritage sites in the area of influence of the Project. | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Financial Management and Procurement Manuals | Description :Ningxia shall apply the Financial Management Manualand the Procurement Manual in implementing the Project for monitoring the entire procurement process and the financialtransactions.| Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Implementation | Description :Ningxia shall not amend, suspend, fail to enforce or waive the Process Framework,the EPG, the PMP or any annual implementation plan. | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Process Framework | Description :Ningxia shall carry out measures for improving the living standards of ProjectAffected Persons in accordance with the Process Framework, and carry out external monitoring and reporting. | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Project Implementation Arrangement and Implementation Units | Description :Throughout implementation, Ningxiashall maintain a Regional Leading Group, Regional Management Office, County Project Management Offices, and Expert Working Groupacceptable to the Bank. | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Project Implementation Manual | Description :Ningxia shall apply and cause the Project Counties to apply in theimplementation of the Project, the Project Implementation Manual, in an efficient and timely manner satisfactory to the Bank. |Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Safeguard Instruments | Description :Ningxia shall implement and cause the Project Counties to implement theProcess Framework, Environmental Protection Guidelines, andPest Management Plan, in a manner satisfactory to the Bank. | Frequency:Yearly

Finance Agreement :Straw Market Analysis | Description :Ningxia shall, periodically, carry out a market analysis of the local strawmarkets in order to monitor price developments and any market distortions from the extensive procurement of straw. | Frequency:Yearly

Finance Agreement :Treatment Models and Technical Standards | Description :Ningxia shall cause the Project Counties to implementand protect plantation and vegetation rehabilitation according to agreed models and standards and adequate land managementarrangements. | Frequency :Yearly

Ningxia shall cause each Project County to make Output-based Grants to Beneficiaries within its respective jurisdictions inaccordance with eligibility criteria and procedures acceptable to the Bank and set out in the Project Implementation Manual.
